-- Toyota May Introduce New Version of Prius Hybrid in 2016, Sankei Reports
-- Kazuyo Sawa
-- 2010-07-27T22:37:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/toyota-may-introduce-new-version-of-prius-hybrid-in-2016-sankei-reports.html

          
          
             Toyota Motor Corp. may introduce a
new version of its Prius hybrid vehicle in 2016, the Sankei
newspaper reported, without saying where it obtained the
information. The company may produce the model in North America,
the report said.  
